{
  "texts": [
    "Kwasigroch et al. [58] suggest a Deep Learning strategy to simplify the detection of DR.",
    "The most widely used class of Deep Learning algorithms, deep CNNs, succeeded at image recognition and analysis.",
    "Qomariah et al. [81] presented a support vector machinebased Deep Learning algorithm for feature extraction and categorization.",
    "As input features for classification utilizing the support vector machine, they utilize the high-level attributes of the final fully-connected layer depending on transfer learning via CNN.",
    "By employing this technique, it was observed that the classification process using CNN with fine-tuning required less computation time."
  ]
}